th%E1%BB%A7-tr%C3%A1t-su%E1%BA%A5t-nh%C4%A9-khi%E1%BB%83n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-k%C3%BD-c%E1%BA%ADn-tr%C3%ACnh-T%C3%B4-Ho%C3%A1n-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1/poem-OBlyRxjh5TCqFh5dGFYn3g">Mộ thu uổng Bùi Đạo Châu thủ trát, suất nhĩ khiển hứng, ký cận trình Tô Hoán thị ngự - 暮秋枉裴道州手札，率爾遣興，寄近呈蘇渙侍御</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/T%E1%BA%A7m-t%C6%B0-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ni%C3%AAn-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-u87I_yOcxJGwrqgYnu0NXQ">Tầm tư thiếu niên nhật - 尋思少年日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81i-T%C3%A2n-Gi%C3%A1c-La-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-L%E1%BB%8Bch/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-ti%E1%BB%81n-ng%E1%BB%B1-vi%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%A9-y%E1%BA%BFn-t%E1%BB%8Bch-trung-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-c%C3%BA/poem-5eNoK9QmCnasf1K-uaTysw">Tiết tiền ngự viên tứ yến, tịch trung đắc cú - 節前御園賜宴席中得句</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81i-T%C3%A2n-Gi%C3%A1c-La-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-L%E1%BB%8Bch/author-LWiJ3ebJ3gpU86_3bbLouw">Ái Tân Giác La Hoằng Lịch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Ti%E1%BB%83u-vi%C3%AAn-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-gfv01NqeZRc2Zt0sJtTr7w">Tiểu viên kỳ 2 - 小園其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ng%E1%BB%B1-h%C3%A0/poem-rZGPlyD7HZUYOrLB8Yjibg">Vịnh Ngự hà - 詠御河</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br></div>	</div>
